description.narrative: Countries received support to strengthen the use of evidence-based strategies in at least one of the following areas: reproductive, maternal, newborn, child and adolescent health (RMNCAH), Early Childhood Development, Birth Registration, Demand for Immunization, Social Accountability, Harmful practices and social norms, adolescent participation and development. A regional C4D network meeting allowed ESAR countries to exchange learning and good practices.
